Florence Freeman (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Florence_Freeman_(actress) 0 Florence Freeman (July 29, 1911 – April 25, 2000) was an actress in old-time radio. She was known as a "soap opera queen" for her work in daytime serial dramas. Florence_Freeman ( July_29_,_1911 – April_25_,_2000 ) was an_actress in old-time_radio .
